## Documentation Best Practices
- Use clear, concise language
- Include code examples where appropriate
- Maintain consistent formatting across all documentation
- Update documentation when making code changes

## Multi-component Documentation
- Each submodule (`neto/`, `netolib/`, `netoman/`) maintains its own documentation
- Main repository documentation focuses on project orchestration and setup
- Cross-reference between component documentation as needed
